                     <locus from="1r" to="115r"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Second volume of a four-volume set consisting respectively of Pentateuch, Former Prophers, Latter Prophets and Hagiographa; for volumes 1, 3 and 4, see Harley MS 5498a, Harley MS 5498c, and Harley MS 5498d.</p>
                     
                     
                     
