                           <p>Uniform layout. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Ruling with hard-point, pricking sometimes visible.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Judges and Kings begin a new leaf.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Folios 108v-113v left unpunctuated.</p>
                        
                        
                        
